The Tides Beach Club Restaurant | Tides Beach Club Skip to Content Tides Beach Club Accommodations The Hotel Dining TBC Restaurant Our Menus Dining Events Offers All Offers Enhancements Explore Overview Weddings Gallery Book Now Dining Overview Dining Events Menus The Tides Beach Club Restaurant Wine & Dine With Us Savor fresh Maine seafood and a vibrant dining atmosphere at The Tides Beach Club Restaurant, offering delicious local flavors to satisfy every taste. Open seven days a week during the summer, this charming restaurant includes a beautiful beachside porch with awe-inspiring views of the water. Our Menu Our Restaurant The Cuisine The Tides Beach Club features a menu of classic seaside fare, including fresh fish paired with lemon risotto, Maine lobster chowder, clam fritters, and refreshing tomato and burrata salad. Our Restaurant Happy Hour There’s nothing like an ice-cold cocktail in the New England summer sun. Whether it’s fried artichokes or a chilled glass of white wine, join us from 3 pm to 5 pm for the best value on sips and small bites during Happy Hour. 0 1 Our Hours Dinner: Daily , 11:30AM-9PM Lunch: Saturdays + Sundays, 11:30AM-3PM Happy Hour: Daily, 3-5PM Live Entertainment: Sundays, 3-5PM *Please note: Parking at The Tides Beach Club is for hotel guests only. Guests dining at the restaurant will need to pay for Goose Rocks Beach Parking Dining Reservations Our KRC hotel guests receive exclusive access to dining reservations at our Kennebunkport Resort Collection restaurants . Contact us at stay@tidesbeachclubmaine.com for assistance in securing advance reservations at most of our unique restaurants. Please note: The Boathouse Restaurant and The Dory do not take reservations.
